
== Enable to start your product with right mouse click
	
		You can also add the
		_pde nature_
		to your project in which you placed the product configuration file,
		if
		you want to
		be
		able
		to start your product via a
		right-click on the
		product
		and by selecting
		menu:
			<guimenu>Run-as</guimenu>
			<guisubmenu>Eclipse Application</guisubmenu>
		</menuchoice>
		.
	
	NOTE:
		
			The
			_Package Explorer_
			view
			may have a filter set for
			_.*resources_
			. You can modify this filter via the view menu as depicted in the
			following screenshot.
		
		
image::removefilterfordotfiles10.png"
						scale="40[Remove filter,pdfwidth=60%]
		


	</note>

	
		For this
		purpose
		remove
		the filter in the
		_Package Explorer_
		view
		for files starting with . (dot) and modify the
		_.project_
		file to the following.
	
	
		<programlisting language="xml">
			<xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
				parse="text" href="./examples/firstrcp/project" />
		</programlisting>
	

